actions.text: Referred to Senate Committee on Finance.

official_title: A bill to prohibit the withdrawal of merchandise from a customs bonded warehouse for exportation pursuant to retail sales unless such warehouse is located in close proximity to a port, airport, or border crossing station.

summary.text: Prohibits the withdrawal of merchandise from a customs bonded warehouse for exportation pursuant to retail sales unless such warehouse is located in close proximity to a port, airport, or border crossing station.
